      "components": [
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-obsidian-slate:#2d2f33;--color-canvas-white:#ffffff;--color-warm-mist:#f3f3ee;--color-ash-concrete:#e8e8de;--color-deep-pewter:#2a2a25;--color-steel-gray:#c2c2be;--color-soft-stone:#69695d;--color-faded-quartz:#9c9c90;--color-neon-zest:#f43e01;--color-deep-ember:#c23101;--font-space-grotesk:'Space Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif;--font-ibm-plex-mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;background:var(--color-warm-mist);padding:48px 40px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:32px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-ibm-plex-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--color-neon-zest);margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;\">Inference is fuel for AI</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:36px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.0;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--color-obsidian-slate);margin:0;\">Groq delivers fast, low cost inference that doesn't flake when things get real.</h2>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row;gap:16px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:var(--color-neon-zest);color:var(--color-canvas-white);font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.02em;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:1000px;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--color-canvas-white);white-space:nowrap;\">Get Started</a>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:transparent;color:var(--color-obsidian-slate);font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.02em;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:1000px;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--color-obsidian-slate);white-space:nowrap;\">Learn More</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Primary CTA Button Group",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-obsidian-slate:#2d2f33;--color-canvas-white:#ffffff;--color-warm-mist:#f3f3ee;--color-ash-concrete:#e8e8de;--color-deep-pewter:#2a2a25;--color-steel-gray:#c2c2be;--color-soft-stone:#69695d;--color-faded-quartz:#9c9c90;--color-neon-zest:#f43e01;--color-deep-ember:#c23101;--font-space-grotesk:'Space Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif;--font-ibm-plex-mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;background:var(--color-warm-mist);padding:48px 40px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-ibm-plex-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--color-neon-zest);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px 0;\">Don't take our word for it.</p>\n  <div style=\"background:var(--color-ash-concrete);padding:32px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:46px;font-weight:400;line-height:0.9;color:var(--color-neon-zest);margin-top:-4px;flex-shrink:0;\">&ldquo;</span>\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:17px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.57;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--color-obsidian-slate);margin:0;\">We optimized our infrastructure to its limits – but the breakthrough came with GroqCloud. Overnight, our chat speed surged 7.41x while costs fell by 89%. I was stunned. So, we tripled our token consumption. We simply can't get enough.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-ibm-plex-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--color-soft-stone);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0;\">Nicolas Bustamante, CEO, Fintool</p>\n      <div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-obsidian-slate);border-radius:5px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-canvas-white);line-height:1;\">F</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Testimonial Card",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-obsidian-slate:#2d2f33;--color-canvas-white:#ffffff;--color-warm-mist:#f3f3ee;--color-ash-concrete:#e8e8de;--color-deep-pewter:#2a2a25;--color-steel-gray:#c2c2be;--color-soft-stone:#69695d;--color-faded-quartz:#9c9c90;--color-neon-zest:#f43e01;--color-deep-ember:#c23101;--font-space-grotesk:'Space Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif;--font-ibm-plex-mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;background:var(--color-warm-mist);padding:48px 40px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#2e2e29;padding:40px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;\">\n    <div style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;height:28px;\">\n      <svg width=\"20\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 28\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M11.5 2L2 16h8l-1.5 10L18 12h-8L11.5 2z\" fill=\"#f43e01\"/></svg>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:32px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--color-warm-mist);margin:0;\">Others rely on GPUs alone. Our edge? Custom silicon.</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.57;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--color-faded-quartz);margin:0;\">Groq pioneered the LPU in 2016, the first chip purpose-built for inference. Every design choice focuses on keeping intelligence fast and affordable.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:var(--color-neon-zest);color:var(--color-canvas-white);font-family:var(--font-space-grotesk);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.02em;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:1000px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;\">Learn More</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
